abstract: United States national wrestling team, competing at world qualifying event in Mongolia, earns three more spots at 2016 Olympics in Rio de Janeiro; team will compete in 12 of 18 classes.

headline.main: U.S. Wrestling Team Earns Olympic Berths

snippet: The United States wrestling team will compete in 12 of the 18 weight classes at the Rio de Janeiro Olympics after earning three more spots this weekend.
lead_paragraph: The United States wrestling team will compete in 12 of the 18 weight classes at the Rio de Janeiro Olympics after earning three more spots this weekend.
